Question: Develop an argument for or against using a cellphone while driving.
Answer:
It is a long time for people to debate whether we should or should not use a cellphone when we are driving. i prefer we should carefully examine what is right to use. For example, if we are just calling the other people in the car, it may be ok since people are usually able to do it. But for instance, if people are texting other people when driving a car, it is very dangerous.